<%= render Primer::BlankslateComponent.new(
  title: "Gist unavailable due to DMCA takedown.",
  narrow: true,
  mt: 4,
  text: :left,
) do %>
  <p>
    This gist is currently disabled due to a DMCA takedown notice. We have disabled public access to the gist. The notice has been <%= link_to "publicly posted", gist.access.dmca_url, class: "Link--inTextBlock" %>.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you are the gist owner, and you believe that your gist was disabled as a result of mistake or misidentification, you have the right to file a counter notice and have the gist reinstated. Our help articles provide more details on our <%= link_to "DMCA takedown policy", "#{GitHub.help_url}/articles/dmca-takedown-policy", class: "Link--inTextBlock" %> and <%= link_to "how to file a counter notice", "#{GitHub.help_url}/articles/guide-to-submitting-a-dmca-counter-notice", class: "Link--inTextBlock" %>. If you have any questions about the process or the risks in filing a counter notice, we suggest that you consult with a lawyer.
  </p>
<% end %>
